    <item>
      <title>软着陆并非不可避免。行业轮动是</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-01-31/soft-landing-isn-t-inevitable-but-sector-rotation-is</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储一月份的利率决定是在投资者完全相信软着陆说法之际做出的。这样的结果应该有助于股市避免另一场熊市。但当经济衰退确实到来时，极端的市场集中度表明，积极的行业轮换策略将获得回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-01-31/soft-landing-isn-t-inevitable-but-sector-rotation-is</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 17:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
